          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "この煮込み料理には、旨味の強い牛肉の切り出しをたっぷり使うのがコツなんだ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "焼肉屋で、色々な部位の切り出しを盛り合わせで頼んでみた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "カレーを作るために、スーパーで安かった牛の切り出し肉を買ってきたよ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "starting to speak",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "長年抱えていた悩みを、ついに親友に切り出すことができた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "会議の終盤、彼は重い口を開き、プロジェクトの遅延について切り出した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "子供が初めて「ママ」と言った時、その場にいた全員が感動して、その小さな切り出しに耳を澄ました。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 5,
        "gloss": "extraction (of a portion of a media file)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
